<h1>Carthas</h1>
<p>House Carthas' members include all the major merchants in the Empire. Composed mostly of Sea Dwarves, Humans, and Halflings, Carthas controls nearly all the flow of goods within the Empire. They negotiate contracts with farmers, craftsmen, and other Houses, constantly attempting to use the collective power of their members to keep the prices low on numerous goods. While House Carthas' power is great, it is somewhat offset by the power of the Houses with which they are forced to negotiate. House Argentus, Ilmath, and Brios will only allow the cost of their labors to be driven so low.</p>
<h2>Ranks</h2>
<ul>
<li>Peddler</li>
<li>Salesperson</li>
<li>Mistre Merchant</li>
</ul>
