<h3>House Scion(3)</h3>
<h1>Ilmath</h1>
<p>The House of crafters, Ilmath is the combined will of smiths, carpenters, weavers, and more, all throughout the Empire. Another House that is composed mostly of Humans and Dwarves, Ilmath also has what some may find to be a surprising number of Orcs and Half-Orcs, mostly representing the metal-smithing crafts. A number of succesful weavers come from Gnomish stock, and Halflings and Goblins are both known for intricate wood-work. Dwarves and Goblins dominate the jewelry industry. Humans tend to fill in the more average, everyday products, though a few human crafters do rise to artisan level.</p>
