<h3>House Scion(3)</h3>
<h1>Aeth</h1>
<p>House Aeth deals in the darker side of business. Mostly known for its black market trade of stolen and illicit goods, the bulk of Aeth's political power actually comes from its person removal services. Aeth assasins are feared throughout the Empire. Nothing ruins a person's day like finding out someone has hired House Aeth to kill you. Mostly Humans, Orcs, and Half-Orcs, Aeth also has a smattering of Elves, Half-Elves, and a small handful of Gnomes. Aeth has never had, and most likely never will have, any Halfling members. There is a bitter feud between the two groups.</p>
