<h3>House Scion(3)</h3>
<h1>Brios</h1>
<p>Home of artists, musicians, poets, and storytellers, House Brios is also sometimes known as the House of the Aesthetics. The House has equal parts Humans, Halflings, Goblins, Shidhe, and Half-Elves, as well as a smattering of the other races as well. Legend states the House was originally founded by Bria, but within the House it is spoken of as being founded by one of her apostles, a nameless bard who chronicled the rise of the Chrysanthia Pantheon.</p>
