<h3>House Scion(3)</h3>
<h1>Lupanar</h1>
<p>Colloquially known as the House of Mortal Pleasure, Lupanar is home to sex workers and hedonists throughout the Empire. Every race is counted in their ranks, though Elves, Half-Elves, and Sidhe are represented slightly more than the others. The House controls brothels, drug dens, and addiction recovery houses in every major and minor city in the Empire. They believe in the balanced and moderate indulgence of all physical desires, and are a vocal proponent of therapy through monitored drug use. They serve as the Empire's de-facto psychologists.</p>
