<h1>Canae</h1>
<p>House Canae is mostly home to Sidhe, Elves, Half-elves, Humans, and Gnomes, with a small handful of Halflings, Half-orcs, and Dwarves. They are the guardians of arcane knowledge, and boast many acolytes and followers of Canaedus.</p>
